channel.title: First Photoshop sig try, yes im ready to be shot down*
channel.description:
so ive been fooling around on photoshop, i definitely do [u][b]NOT[/b][/u] consider myself good, im horrible lol...i just decided to post it cause im proud, and im happy with my work, but i expect my stuff to be called shit and what not, ive read a few other peoples posts and i know who to look out for lol, but other than that cc is very much appreciated & needed.
what i think is bad- 1. the lighting could be maybe dimmer and in a diffrent location. 2. its smuged to much, he almost is covered up and his guns are barely noticable. 3. The colors are to dull, even though i went for a "coming up out of the smoke" idea, its to much. 4. The stars....i dunno lol. it was in the tut so i followed it, they dont seem to bad, but its just me. 5. Basically everything lol....
i followed this [tut]- http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rTDkKqXNIgI&feature=fvw **sorry if i cant post links.. my photobucket- [url=http://s973.photobucket.com/albums/ae213/t_litten_2009/]http://s973.photobucket.com/albums/ae213/t_litten_2009/[/url]
here it is, i hope its not the worst thing youve ever seen lol... [img]http://i973.photobucket.com/albums/ae213/t_litten_2009/firstevercopy.png[/img]
second one- again same tut [img]http://i973.photobucket.com/albums/ae213/t_litten_2009/Secondcopy.png[/img]
Third try late last night, uploaded it today around 6am- i went with a no light, and a wind effect with invert. hope you like :/ [img]http://i973.photobucket.com/albums/ae213/t_litten_2009/coolhalofinish.png[/img] **Edit- dont understand why my name is gone, now im gonna get called a ripper lol....
